<span id="freeTextContainer6686614035877025493">Another train wreck story, one you can see coming. Majority of my review is going to be a spoiler because i just couldn&apos;t with this book. Pity i&apos;m going to have to restrain myself for the Zon review.<br/><br/>Joseph aka Stone aka Tiny although he hates that name. Maddison aka maddie. These are the main characters we have and who this story is about. <br/><a class='jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction'>(view spoiler)</a><span class='spoilerContainer' style='display: none'>[ Joseph grew up with his dad, a druggie good for nothing addict, who after 14 years decide he has had enough. I&apos;m surprised he lived to the end</span></span>
  <span id="freeText6686614035877025493" style="display:none">Another train wreck story, one you can see coming. Majority of my review is going to be a spoiler because i just couldn't with this book. Pity i'm going to have to restrain myself for the Zon review.<br /><br />Joseph aka Stone aka Tiny although he hates that name. Maddison aka maddie. These are the main characters we have and who this story is about. <br /><a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[ Joseph grew up with his dad, a druggie good for nothing addict, who after 14 years decide he has had enough. I'm surprised he lived to the end of this book because he was diagnosed with lung cancer when stone was 13, but managed to make it 8 years still smoking, getting high etc, etc no medication. However he dropped the kid off at this trailer park saying it was his mother place because he couldn't take care of him anymore. So Joseph goes to meet this woman only to meet Maddie for the first time at 11, outside the same house where he declares he is her brother, but even at 14 the kid has the hots for this kid yeah. We of course have no clue if they are actually related because the mother is also surprise, surprise a prostitute, and a druggie and can't remember Joseph dad apart from he was a shit fuck. So we go through the whole book wondering are they related or not. <br /><br />Fast forward five years from initial meeting and we find out that Joseph is in Jail,from saving Maddie it seems from some lowlife( we really don't see a full picture here of what the heck happens basically someone dies) he is somehow supporting Maddie and their other siblings three of them from prison. He seems to be getting money from some guy name Sly. Stuff happens, but next scene is a year later and Maddie hasn't been to see Joseph and he's all angry but think she may be dead because of stuff he did etc. who know basically a short fuse dude , until good luck he getts released early but on probation for a few years. Immediately he heads to find Maddie using infor from a cop who has been good to both him and Maddie.<br /><br />Maddie, it seems has been a busy girl, she has a good job by the grace of her boss Andrew , but of course they are catches. She apparently acts as his slave( yes all the connotations except no full on sex because she is waiting until she turns 19) we know cock sucking involved because it happens a few times., but she hints they may be other things. <br /><br />Of course they are happy to see each other, she is happy Stone is back in her life, but she is still in love with him and wants him and vice versa. She eventually tells him about her deal with Andrew, and of course come the 19th birthday and she goes out and have sex with him because he is kinda blackmailing her. yes, he faked certain things for her and threatens the kids etc. She then finds out he was Sly's brother and he knows she killed him. We find this out when Joseph checks her pussy when she comes back from the devirginising session. <br /><br />But he still loves her, even though we think he is kinda sleeping with her friend and sometimes babysitter Clarissa who Joseph of course finds extra hot. it all comes to a lovely cliff hanger when Andrew gets angry and goes over to her place smashes up Clarissa, takes one of the kids and wants Maddie in exchange. She and Stone goes over to his place where he gets chocked off by the bodyguard, she gets smashed around, Daniel the baby brother gets his arm in a cast until Andrew gives him to Stone to take while his prize Maddie stays for most likely another rough sex session, not that she has much choice at this point because really all the cards are in Andrew court and he has the money and the clout to get them both fucked over.<br /><br />h and just to ad to all this horrible shit, one of the siblings young Dylan unfortunately dies from leukemia after Stone is released from Prison. So bad, bad, bad depressing shit happening to two people who can't seem to pull it together to save themselves or the kids depending on them. <br /><br />Not sure i want to read book 2, but the cliffie was good so thank goodness the series is in KU, as this book was an ARC. I got tired of Stone's overreacting to everything, for someone who had been in Jail and wants the best his temper just kept getting the better of him. To be honest the whole thing just annoyed the crap out of me but i'm a glutton for punishment so will likely read the other part <a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[ <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span> <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span></span>
