<div id="review_2172345560" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2172345560" />
    <a title="Kymberly Holland" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/11084042-kymberly-holland"><img alt="Kymberly Holland" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2172345560?book_show_action=true">Nov 02, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kymberly Holland" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kymberly Holland" href="/user/show/11084042-kymberly-holland">Kymberly Holland</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2172345560" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7231227684306750368">An interwoven tale of forbidden love.<br/>This story will grab you and hold you tight as your thrust into a dark world full of emotional abuse and terrors that really exist in our lives today. Horrors that most people never look up long enough to see it. Ms. Rose has brought to the light the darker, seamier side of the world and introduces us to Stone and Maddie, two lost youths growing up too fast and trying to make the best of what life has dished out for them. Both are from drug addicted parents. </span>
  <span id="freeText7231227684306750368" style="display:none">An interwoven tale of forbidden love.<br />This story will grab you and hold you tight as your thrust into a dark world full of emotional abuse and terrors that really exist in our lives today. Horrors that most people never look up long enough to see it. Ms. Rose has brought to the light the darker, seamier side of the world and introduces us to Stone and Maddie, two lost youths growing up too fast and trying to make the best of what life has dished out for them. Both are from drug addicted parents. Both are struggling to stay safe and grow to adulthood. But Stone finds himself in the protector position and his feelings for Maddie are blooming into more...<br />Maddie is struggling with responsibility...she has her siblings to worry about and she can only live day by day, never knowing what the future will hold. Her closeness to Stone gradually grows into something more... something that warms her soul but is frowned upon by society.<br />The emotional roller coaster ride you will be on with this tale is well worth the price for the ride. Ms. Rose's world is fraught with all the emotions and then some... but underneath it all is Love. A Love for an eternity. You will cry, scream, laugh and cry some more. Her storytelling talents are phenomenal! This is the first time reading her work and I will be back for more. A solid 5 stars on an epic tale of heartache and joy!</span>
  <a data-text-id="7231227684306750368" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


