<span id="freeTextContainer18107319049049338746">This book is a story of love, hope, sadness, betrayal, and most of all loyalty. <br/><br/>Stone and Madison have both lived horrible lives and all they want is happiness. <br/><br/>I really enjoyed how Angel Rose wrote a story about a taboo topic and went into detail about what each character had lived with from childhood to adulthood. Their upbringing was so detailed that I had tears for them. No one should have to live life feeling unwanted or unloved. <br/><br/>Stone and Madison were all each other had. And would do anyth</span>
  <span id="freeText18107319049049338746" style="display:none">This book is a story of love, hope, sadness, betrayal, and most of all loyalty. <br /><br />Stone and Madison have both lived horrible lives and all they want is happiness. <br /><br />I really enjoyed how Angel Rose wrote a story about a taboo topic and went into detail about what each character had lived with from childhood to adulthood. Their upbringing was so detailed that I had tears for them. No one should have to live life feeling unwanted or unloved. <br /><br />Stone and Madison were all each other had. And would do anything for each other even while separated. <br />Stone and Maddie crave what is forbidden. <br /><br />What lengths would you go to be with someone you knew was forbidden? </span>
  <a data-text-id="18107319049049338746" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
