<span id="freeTextContainer5459700372740739067">If you are looking for a realistic, dark and forbidden romance then look no further. Angel Rose does an excellent job at portraying the hard subjects that no one ever wants to think about. There is so much raw, gritty emotion in this book. The author brings it all to you with Stone; poverty, loss, strength when you didn&apos;t think possible and a forbidden love so powerful that it is unwavering even in the toughest of times. You will see the characters, Stone and Maddie, go through so much in this b</span>
  <span id="freeText5459700372740739067" style="display:none">If you are looking for a realistic, dark and forbidden romance then look no further. Angel Rose does an excellent job at portraying the hard subjects that no one ever wants to think about. There is so much raw, gritty emotion in this book. The author brings it all to you with Stone; poverty, loss, strength when you didn't think possible and a forbidden love so powerful that it is unwavering even in the toughest of times. You will see the characters, Stone and Maddie, go through so much in this book and the author makes it feel like you are part of their struggles as if they were your own. This is my first book by this author and I look forward to reading more from her catalogue. </span>
