        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2055441752" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1877575890946594607">Stone and Maddie are thrown together in a life neither of them asked for. Their childhood is surrounded by addiction, drugs, and neglect. When they&apos;re finally old enough to have some control over their lives, they find themselves drawn to each other. But are they related? No one seems to have clear answers. This is a heartbreaking story, one where you have to weather the storm to get through the pain and anguish. It&apos;s beautiful but emotional, and I would love to know what happens next!<br/><br/>I voluntar</span>
  <span id="freeText1877575890946594607" style="display:none">Stone and Maddie are thrown together in a life neither of them asked for. Their childhood is surrounded by addiction, drugs, and neglect. When they're finally old enough to have some control over their lives, they find themselves drawn to each other. But are they related? No one seems to have clear answers. This is a heartbreaking story, one where you have to weather the storm to get through the pain and anguish. It's beautiful but emotional, and I would love to know what happens next!<br /><br />I voluntarily reviewed an advance reader copy of this book.</span>
