<span id="freeTextContainer255461312294696219">Angel Rose is a new author to me and one I will continue to follow. I gave it 4 stars only because it needs a good clean editing and no other reason. That being said. This story line is different then most I have read, but is really in some peoples everyday life. A little dark kinda romance, but not as bad as you would think. Just be open minded and read all the books. It’s a great story line that you can actually picture happening in real life, because it does. Stone is that bad boy you are jus</span>
  <span id="freeText255461312294696219" style="display:none">Angel Rose is a new author to me and one I will continue to follow. I gave it 4 stars only because it needs a good clean editing and no other reason. That being said. This story line is different then most I have read, but is really in some peoples everyday life. A little dark kinda romance, but not as bad as you would think. Just be open minded and read all the books. It’s a great story line that you can actually picture happening in real life, because it does. Stone is that bad boy you are just not sure about. An poor Maddie you can’t help but to love her and her siblings. </span>
