        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2495030470" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15009251407658957452">Wow this is one Emotional Rollercoaster! There was times I was crying so hard I wanted to skip parts, but I pushed through and survived this book. This is for sure a dark read! I was hooked right away! Stone and Maddie have an amazing love story to tell. By the end of this book I was dreading the end. I was kind of sad to read the last page. These characters are battling a lot, throw in some taboo topics for some young adults and the struggle is definitely real! I just waned to gather Maddie and</span>
  <span id="freeText15009251407658957452" style="display:none">Wow this is one Emotional Rollercoaster! There was times I was crying so hard I wanted to skip parts, but I pushed through and survived this book. This is for sure a dark read! I was hooked right away! Stone and Maddie have an amazing love story to tell. By the end of this book I was dreading the end. I was kind of sad to read the last page. These characters are battling a lot, throw in some taboo topics for some young adults and the struggle is definitely real! I just waned to gather Maddie and Stone up at times and hug them tight. This is must read! </span>
