<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer4307565561005080823">Dark.Realistic.Emotional<br/>Not your ordinary love stories<br/><br/>Angel Rose has been writing dark romance since 2014. She is driven to create characters from the forgotten world which surrounds us all. The unlucky, the downtrodden, and those who simply never had a chance. Despite the life they find themselves in or, perhaps because of it, you feel for them and their struggles. You want them to succeed. You w</span>
  <span id="freeText4307565561005080823" style="display:none">Dark.Realistic.Emotional<br />Not your ordinary love stories<br /><br />Angel Rose has been writing dark romance since 2014. She is driven to create characters from the forgotten world which surrounds us all. The unlucky, the downtrodden, and those who simply never had a chance. Despite the life they find themselves in or, perhaps because of it, you feel for them and their struggles. You want them to succeed. You want them to catch the proverbial "break" they deserve. The reader needs them to win for once in their lives. It is romance which pulls her stories together. The hope of love as the last bastion of happiness for those who have none is what her readers crave. She forces those who turn a page to believe that love really can conquer all. <br /><br />If you're ready to go where you have never been before and are ready to believe in love again, Angel Rose will take you where you need to go. Angel lives in New York with her loving husband of many years. A happy, working mother of two, Mrs. Rose enjoys spending time with her family when she is not writing. <br /><br />Editorial Reviews:<br /><br />Murder in Cazenovia By Angel Rose<br />Rated it 5 Stars! It was amazing!<br />"I was so in love with this book right away. I was done with this book in a day and half, I could not put it down. This book is full of twist and turns that I did not see coming. Just when I thought I had it all figured out Boom something else happens that proved me wrong." -Laid-back Book Bitches(Blog)<br /><br />Stone book 1<br />Love me some Stone! 4 Stars!<br />July 4, 2018<br />Format: Kindle Edition<br />Angel Rose is a new author to me and one I will continue to follow." -True Grit Book Blogs<br /><br />Stone Book 2<br />5 Stars! Heartbreaking...<br />July 4, 2018<br />Format: Kindle Edition<br />"Okay I have read some of the different reviews and honestly just stop with the incest crap until you read all 3 of the books! Besides that open your DAM eyes it happens more then you think in the world all around us! ."<br />-True Grit Book Blogs<br /><br /><br />Stone Book 3<br />Love you Stone!<br />July 4, 2018<br />Format: Kindle Edition<br />This book truly broke my heart with everything that has happened in the 1st 2 books! I even messaged the author and told her I didn't like her any more!! A complete lie, but she does seem to know how to keep you on your toes and rip your heart out at the same time! <br />-True Grit Book Blogs</span>
